<lyrics>[V1]
 1- jamālu rabĩnā bahī̃̊
 ạảb̊raʿu min̊ banī ạl̊basẖar̊
 wamitẖ̊lu tufãạḥiⁿ sẖahī̃̊
 mā baẙna ạảsẖ̊jāri ạl̊waʿar̊

[V2]
 2- wafīhi rāḥaẗuⁿ lanā
 fī ẓilĩhi yaḥ̊lū ạl̊julūs̊
 ạảtẖ̊māruhu ladẖãtunā
 ḥuḍūruhu yur̊wī ạlnũfūs̊

[V3]
 3- wās̊muhu duh̊nuⁿ muh̊raquⁿ
 wāảṭ̊yabu min̊ kulĩ ṭīb̊
 ại̹nãhu yasūʿu ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 wās̊muhu ḥul̊wuⁿ waʿajīb̊

[V4]
 4- wamuʿ̊lamuⁿ fī rib̊waẗiⁿ
 wafīhi ạảʿ̊jabu ạlṣĩfāt̊
 waḥal̊quhu ḥalạwaẗuⁿ
 wakulũhu musẖ̊tahayāt̊

[V5]
 5- fadẖalika ạlsẖãkẖ̊ṣu ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 hūa ʿarīsunā ạl̊waḥīd̊
 wasanuzafũ ʿan̊ qarīb̊
 lahu fī ʿur̊sihi ạl̊majīd̊</lyrics>
<title>jmạl rbnạ bhy</title>
</song>